name: Rapidata-term-api
body:
RapiData-TermAPI
================
## API Specification:

Request URL: /datasets/find?list[term1,term2...]


Response: 
```xml
<datasets>
	<dataset>
		<title>
			Title
		<title>
		<link>
			Link
		</link>
		<description>
			Description
		</description>
	<dataset>
		.
		.
		.
</dataset>
```
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
